{"tid":1951664,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇Freitag袋同好﹖","createTime":"2020-03-31T06:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T18:52:53.000Z","uid":297099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b5adad239156d6ca326523eab6f06a7a19533b89","tid":1951664,"uid":297099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:11:31.000Z","msg":"小弟未有咁高級數去買LV，但又唔想揹個普普通通一街都係撞晒款既袋，所以十年前開始用Freitag。雖然睇落好似殘殘舊舊，但佢既環保概念好好，每個袋都獨一無二，就算同款，但pattern都一定唔同。<br />\n<br />\n話說小弟係十年前一次去日本，係東京新國立美術館見到依個牌子，當時見佢啲袋設計得幾靚，但又未識係咩牌子，我仲傻到走去問sales有冇新一個......<br />\n<br />\n返到黎香港就去search下依個牌子，結果好啱我心水。雖然啲friend成日問我做咩揹個咁殘個袋，我都不嫌其煩咁向佢介紹下Freitag。<br />\n<br />\n唔知依度又有冇Freitag同好呢﹖不如大家又分享下點識依個牌子，同埋有邊款袋﹖<br />\n<br />\n我先，我一共有兩個，一個係Messenger F12 DRAGNET，藍色，另一個係laptop袋，個款停產左，唔記得叫咩model。兩個袋都係2011年係置地Harvey Nichols買，用左9年喇，但真係除左外表係殘殘地外，完全冇穿冇爛。近幾年係日本讀書，我帶左個laptop袋過黎用，日日粗用都仲未爛，所以真心推介畀各位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REb5TcQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREb5TcQ.png&h=9f2dec8c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n（利申：非打手文）"},{"pid":"e815c1d613285c42754136e59c073037880ac656","tid":1951664,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T03:34:49.000Z","msg":"好撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3fdb79dd5efa04439309b5946380c73edf1471","tid":1951664,"uid":297099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e815c1d613285c42754136e59c073037880ac656","tid":1951664,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T03:34:49.000Z","msg":"好撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"依個係佢STYLE，唔係我刻意整污糟。"},{"pid":"daa090cc9dce303c2b52acb7422ec20260d798c7","tid":1951664,"uid":286908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:50:25.000Z","msg":"Freitag好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打識貨<br />\n<br />\n我D frd都覺得我好奇怪<br />\n但我以為香港好多人識添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ujGLZ6q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FujGLZ6q.png&h=790d3616&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"185b7fd20b982830524e25ad006c2a6229aaf834","tid":1951664,"uid":286908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:52:53.000Z","msg":"袋既話我買左 LASSIE，DEXTER，FRINGE同埋MAURICE<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}